h1. accept

h2. Purpose

Sets the @Accept@ header of the request.

h2. Examples

{code}
new RequestBuilder().get {
    uri = "example.com"
    accept = "text/html"
}
{code}

h2. Description

Sets the @Accept@ header of the outgoing request. This option informs the server that the client expects a certain @Content-Type@ in the response.
